{"tid":771762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港既所有問題都係來自兩個問題","createTime":"2018-08-08T08:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T12:47:17.000Z","uid":52817,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c40bbc195f3754746a11cf3f3af6b4e26413ee","tid":771762,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"我發現香港既所有問題，無論係醫療事故、樓價、車位、港鐵工程、尖咀大媽、樂壇沒落、產業單一、鉛水等等等等，其實都來自兩個問題：<br />\n<br />\n1. 強制輸入人口<br />\n2. 中資成為主流<br />\n<br />\n而問題2既根源其實同樣來自於問題1，所以香港其實只有一個問題。<br />\n<br />\n但係到左而家，就算解決問題1都解決唔到香港既問題。"},{"pid":"261e399940f81a739d5e25327344d4268f25d9fe","tid":771762,"uid":63588,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:41:18.000Z","msg":"係窮呀屌你個閪"},{"pid":"c5c454d94c0ae140dbcbabab38577158264ea0bf","tid":771762,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"香港只有一個問題(問題1)<br />\n<br />\n--&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">香港既問題</span> = <span style=\"color: blue;\">問題1</span>......(1)<br />\n<br />\n但係到左而家，就算解決<span style=\"color: blue;\">問題1</span>都解決唔到<span style=\"color: red;\">香港既問題</span>。.....(2)<br />\n<br />\nsubstitute (1) into (2)<br />\n<br />\n但係到左而家，就算解決<span style=\"color: blue;\">問題1</span>都解決唔到<span style=\"color: blue;\">問題1</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ???"},{"pid":"e7a6e83ba24752b18326baae29602934c0bee0b2","tid":771762,"uid":94828,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"可以夾埋做一個問題<br />\n就係中共"},{"pid":"bfb2eb91d4192f4126263732bc9ebc8acfb5e290","tid":771762,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"係政府問題"},{"pid":"0be320d82896ccc2b7b08368e9d82df761cf270e","tid":771762,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime